name: Denis Dits
description:
I have a lot to offer the right person; I know how to treat that special woman in my life. I am emotionally secure and looking for the same. I am NOT a game player! I am easy going and have a big heart. I am intelligent, caring, have a sense of humor (mostly sarcastic) and am 100% loyal.
I am looking for a woman who is active and who has self confidence in hermself and she is interested in dating one quality person. My motto is never look back, always look forward and everyone deserves to be happy. I am Silly and Sweet, Sassy and Classy, Mature and Serious, Playful with Good Intentions, like to laugh and enjoy life.
